Commissioner Danga Women’s rights advocate, Dorothy Njemanze, has asked Kogi State governor, Yahaya Bello, to sack his Commissioner for Water Resources, Abdulmumimu Danga, who assaulted and raped a young lady in the state. Danga had abducted, assaulted and raped Elizabeth Oyeniyi, the victim, for asking him to take care of his family.



